astria|2006}} concerning Marcu, including the quote from an unnamed "well-known mathematician" that "Marcu is a notorious plagiarist".</ref> He had submitted a manuscript for publication that was a word-for-word replicate of a published paper written by another author.<ref>Karl Strambach and Ferdinand D. Veldkamp, "[http://www.springerlink.com/content/k7rm674498665241/ Editorial statement]", ''Geometriae Dedicata'' '''32''' (1989), p. 253; see also {{Zbl|0701.51004}} and {{MR|1038400}}.</ref>
